Package com.kormapper.model

Class KORMapperNEW

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kormapper.model.KORMapperNEW

  • public class KORMapperNEW
extends java.lang.Object
    Karui Object Relational Mapper This class provides all of the key features of the KORMapper-API. -- Query -- Insert -- Update -- Delete
    Version:
    0.0.3 Added Modes to KORGenerator DEFAULT and IGNORE (see ON CONFLICT clause)
    0.0.2 Fixed NullPointerException when reflecting fields with null values. Improved exception throwing.
    0.0.1 Initial version
    Author:
    leonhardmuellauer
